title: Mermaid Test All Diagrams
author: asophila
created: 20260427
tags: [[mermaid test]]
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

This tiddler tests every diagram type supported by Mermaid 11.14.0 in the mermaid-tw5 plugin.

!! Flowchart

<$mermaid text='''
graph TD
    A[Start] --> B{Decision}
    B -->|Yes| C[Action 1]
    B -->|No| D[Action 2]
    C --> E[End]
    D --> E
'''/>

!! Sequence Diagram

<$mermaid text='''
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Alice
    participant B as Bob
    A->>B: Hello Bob
    B-->>A: Hi Alice
    A->>B: How are you?
'''/>

!! Class Diagram

<$mermaid text='''
classDiagram
    class Animal {
        +String name
        +makeSound()
    }
    class Dog {
        +fetch()
    }
    Animal <|-- Dog
'''/>

!! State Diagram

<$mermaid text='''
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Running : start
    Running --> Idle : stop
    Running --> Error : fail
    Error --> Idle : reset
'''/>

!! Entity Relationship

<$mermaid text='''
erDiagram
    CUSTOMER ||--o{ ORDER : places
    ORDER ||--|{ LINE_ITEM : contains
    CUSTOMER {
        string name
        string email
    }
'''/>

